refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
arrayopenssl_x509_parse mixedx509cert boolshortnames&true;
openssl_x509_parse returns information about the supplied x509cert, including fields such as subject name, issuer name, purposes, valid from and valid to dates etc.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 The structure of the returned data is (deliberately) not
 yet documented, as it is still subject to change.
